    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded the required levels for MRL 2. The CFD hemolysis pipeline — comprising ANSYS Fluent, the C++ Lagrangian post-processor, Python pre-processing, and MATLAB orchestration — produced RH predictions consistent with in-vitro experimental data at four of five operating points, with conservative overprediction at the fifth. Discretization error (GCI 3.8%) and code verification results support numerical adequacy. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 given the available validation evidence. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
